name: lovely
description:
I made this design with a photo of my friend's face, which I think is one of the most beautiful girls on earth, and I filled it with writings of resistance and love, and all this image is full of words that we can be stuck in for a long time (I wrote in his eyes: I do not want your eyes to get wet, your heart to be upset, your God is the creator of the background) and so I filled the page with love, to give it strength and not to see it upset, because my friend She is not desirable and she does not see herself as beautiful. You give strength to our team to continue our romantic and artistic life, I hope we spread love all over the world.
